700325f-a.text:
East 206th Street, adjoining the S.E. corner of Bainbridge Ave., showing the site upon which was later erected the Epiphany Lutheran Church. The 6-story apartment house, the rear of which is seen, is at the aforementioned corner.

August 25, 1927.

P.L. Sperr.

700456f-a.text:
3161 Bainbridge Ave., at the N.W. corner of East 206th Street.
August 25, 1927.
P. L. Sperr.
